this tells the npc what to say when you click them 

now go to the "minigames" folder within "models"
and add this file
[url=http://up.ht/rqWkr5]lottery.java[/url]

this file controlls basically everything :)

thats pretty much it really if you want to edit how things work ive commented the things you should change, it looks like this:

[code]
public ArrayList<String> lotteryPlayersNames = new ArrayList<String> (); //players (playername)
	public ArrayList<String> unclaimedWinners = new ArrayList<String> (); //Winners that havent claimed
	public int lotteryFund = 0;
	public int prizeAmount = 250; //jackpot amount (in millions)
	public int entryPrice = 2; //price to enter lottery (in millions)
	public int maximumEntryTimes = 5; //maximum times 1 player can enter per draw
	public long lastAnnouncment;
	public int announcmentFrequency = 15; //announcment frequency in mins
[/code]

the 2 arraylists just store information on players and winners that are either offline or had a full invent at the time of the draw.
the int lotteryFund just stores the amount that is currently in the fund
int prizeAmount is editable as the amount needed to draw the lottery and the amount to give the winner (in million, eg 250 = 250m)
entryPrice is the price it costs the player to enter the lottery and the ammount added to the fund each time someone enters
maximumEntryTimes is the amount of times a player can enter before they are blocked from entering, this is reset when the lottery is drawn
announcementFrequency is the time in mins between announcments to the entire server about the fund so far.

hope you all like it

